{"tid":714982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[笑什麼你也是Asian] 遊港問途人哪裏有狗肉及妓女 亞裔美國YouTuber拍片辱港人惹眾怒","createTime":"2018-06-24T05:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T01:30:42.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"404cebfb5b6baf3b1a10c861ed74cc892b87048a","tid":714982,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180623/_2018062318145084515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180623%2F_2018062318145084515.jpg&h=cdb1c977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRiceGum在片中多次嘲諷中國人吃狗肉，更侮辱地問途人「哪裏有貓和狗」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訂閱量逾千萬的美國亞裔YouTuber RiceGum日前上載了來港旅遊的影片，但內容引起強烈爭議！他在片中多次嘲諷中國人吃狗肉，更侮辱地問途人「哪裏有貓和狗」，甚至問途人哪裏可召妓，又做出滋擾他人行為。即使明知網民討厭，他仍不屑地說：「不要再留言叫我返中國，因為我不屬於這裏，我是屬於美國的」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180623/_2018062318145193114.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180623%2F_2018062318145193114.jpg&h=67f8e9fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片初段交代他與拍檔抵達香港機場時，卻在「Hong Kong」字樣旁邊配上日本國旗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180623/_2018062318145245598.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180623%2F_2018062318145245598.jpg&h=49b459b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRiceGum與拍檔又取笑香港人不懂說英語。<br />\n<br />\nRiceGum上周二（12日）在YouTube發布一段名為《Why I Left The Clout House (im sorry)》的影片，記錄了他之前來港兩天的遊記。但影片初段交代他與拍檔抵達香港機場時，卻在「Hong Kong」字樣旁邊配上日本國旗，並取笑香港人不懂說英語。<br />\n<br />\n其後，他開始提到中國人愛吃狗肉，當他在麵店前看到大鍋牛什，即大呼「這鍋是不是狗肉，我覺得很噁心」，隨後他跟拍檔說「我們應該試一試食貓肉」。他又不斷向途人詢問「哪裏有狗？」、「哪裏有貓？」，甚至在麥當勞詢問店員：「這裏有沒有狗？」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180623/_2018062318145217154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180623%2F_2018062318145217154.jpg&h=310bd144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乘搭扶手梯時，拍擋則故意觸碰女士的手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180623/_2018062318145433322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180623%2F_2018062318145433322.jpg&h=6bf757f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他們又向按摩店的派傳單女士，詢問「You guys have happy ending?」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180623/_2018062318145361404.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180623%2F_2018062318145361404.jpg&h=dc0ea506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRiceGum將吃剩一半的雪糕批送給途人，要求途人進食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180623/_2018062318145324911.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180623%2F_2018062318145324911.jpg&h=043aa3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他們更將服裝店內模特兒模型的服飾揭起，露出模型公仔的胸部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180623/_2018062318145422545.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180623%2F_2018062318145422545.jpg&h=451dc48c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他們又闖入正落閘的鞋店，即使店員已告知要關門，拍擋仍拿起鞋子。<br />\n<br />\nRiceGum又四處向街頭籌款人士和派傳單的女士問「哪裏有妓女？」，他甚至向派按摩店傳單的女士詢問「You guys have happy ending?」，即暗問該店有否提供性服務。此外，RiceGum將吃剩一半的雪糕批送給途人，要求途人進食；其拍擋乘搭扶手梯時，則故意觸碰女士的手，又闖入正落閘的鞋店，即使店員已告知要關門，拍擋仍拿起鞋子；他們更將服裝店內模特兒模型的服飾揭起，露出模型公仔的胸部。<br />\n<br />\n片中可見，RiceGum知道不少網民曾留言指罵他，又叫他離開美國返回中國，但他則不屑地說：「不要再留言叫我返回中國，因為我不屬於這裏，我是屬於美國的」。<br />\n<br />\n影片至今已有逾300萬人次收看，逾15萬人讚好，3.7萬人則表示不喜歡。另有不少網民大感憤怒，「好好玩咩？作為香港人，我覺得極度侮辱。你亦都侮辱咗美國人」，另有人批評他沒有禮貌和教養；另有本港網民留言指「我們不會吃狗肉，請做些資料搜集才來這裏」。但亦有網民認為，明知RiceGum是這類型的YouTuber，不喜歡可以不看。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180623/_2018062318145512949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180623%2F_2018062318145512949.jpg&h=a2863a38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRiceGum不屑地說：「不要再留言叫我返回中國，因為我不屬於這裏，我是屬於美國的」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1248273/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1248273%2F&d=pZ%2F3MRUjSYIP6sBkLLJplk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=9232a06c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1248273%2F&h=7301662f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1248273/</a>"},{"pid":"567b600797f6e78a804bcef4eea07ba8ab50f87d","tid":714982,"uid":15815,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"YouTuber 不嬲靠無品發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cf0fedf247661c0ad324271616d112cd74f8e3","tid":714982,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:59:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcdc77707eb811322a224cb7c727c357ac19730a","tid":714982,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劣幣驅良幣"},{"pid":"a6018375d73fff6d8f3338afb7b924254e94d500","tid":714982,"uid":56467,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"咁都仲可以有15萬人like 鬼佬唔係最撚興政治正確咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1f4bbfbfdea4b070187fd3599bbd300fc49da0","tid":714982,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"比狗咬完唔通咬翻隻狗咩<br />\n都唔知佢攻擊咗